NOTICE: This package contains code adapted from the @cloudflare/actors Alarms package.

Original source: https://github.com/cloudflare/actors/tree/main/packages/alarms
Copyright: Cloudflare, Inc.
License: Apache License 2.0 (https://github.com/cloudflare/actors/blob/main/LICENSE)

The adapted code is located in src/alarms.ts and has been modified to:
- Use NADIS dependency injection pattern
- Implement lazy table initialization
- Remove actor-specific dependencies
- Add TypeScript generics for enhanced type safety

The original Apache 2.0 license terms apply to the portions of code derived from
the Cloudflare Actors project. See ATTRIBUTIONS.md in the repository root for
complete attribution details.
